Package com.github.wuic.resource

This package defines what is a resource in WUIC.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
WuicResource Represents a resource provided or to be managed by the WUIC framework.
WuicResourceFactory Abstraction of a factory producing WuicResource objects.
WuicResourceFactoryBuilder Abstraction of a builder producing WuicResourceFactory objects.
WuicResourceProtocol This interface abstracts the way you can read resources through a particular protocol.
